Output docs/public/praxis-demo.gif

Require bun

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Set Padding 50
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8

Sleep 1s

Type "bun gen:domain invoice"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s
Type "tree src/domain/invoice"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s
